<i> Ooh! What can I do?</i>
<i>Who can I blame? Coastal elites?</i>

12:13.275 --> 12:16.693
<i> Avocado socialists? The boy?</i>
<i> [gasps] I've got it.</i>

12:16.695 --> 12:20.155
Mr. Mayor, the blame falls
squarely on the shoulders

12:20.157 --> 12:23.867
Of the crossing guards...'s
inadequate budget.

12:23.869 --> 12:25.410
We need more money!

12:26.413 --> 12:27.579
More money?

12:27.789 --> 12:31.499
More money for training,
for equipment, for overtime,

12:31.501 --> 12:33.918
