on this one.

12:51.062 --> 12:51.936
And now you want
to give him more money?

12:51.938 --> 12:55.064
That makes absolutely no sense.

12:55.066 --> 12:57.108
Listen up, wokester.

12:57.110 --> 12:59.319
Guys like me
are the last line of defense

12:59.321 --> 13:02.113
