back to portland.

13:09.998 --> 13:10.747
[cheering]

13:10.749 --> 13:11.706
Wha...?

13:11.708 --> 13:13.875
All in favor of me

13:13.877 --> 13:15.794
Pulling a political 180
on this issue

13:15.796 --> 13:19.214
And giving the crossing guards
a blank check, say "aye."

13:19.216 --> 13:21.299
-[all] aye.
-Nay.

13:21.301 --> 13:22.634
Somebody get
my enormous checkbook.

13:22.636 --> 13:24.677
[cheering]

13:24.679 --> 13:26.638
